{"id":799645,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Hunt_for_Red_October_(movie)","text":"\"The Hunt for Red October\" is a 1990 American submarine spy-thriller movie directed by John McTiernan, produced by Mace Neufeld, and starring Sean Connery, Alec Baldwin, Scott Glenn, James Earl Jones, and Sam Neill.\nThe film is based of Tom Clancy's 1984 bestselling novel of the same name. It is the first part of the movie series with the protagonist Jack Ryan.","categories":[],"infobox_types":["film"],"annotations":[{"uri":"John_McTiernan","surface_form":"John McTiernan","offset":87},{"uri":"Mace_Neufeld","surface_form":"Mace Neufeld","offset":115},{"uri":"Sean_Connery","surface_form":"Sean Connery","offset":142},{"uri":"Alec_Baldwin","surface_form":"Alec Baldwin","offset":156},{"uri":"Scott_Glenn","surface_form":"Scott Glenn","offset":170},{"uri":"James_Earl_Jones","surface_form":"James Earl Jones","offset":183},{"uri":"Sam_Neill","surface_form":"Sam Neill","offset":205},{"uri":"Tom_Clancy","surface_form":"Tom Clancy","offset":237},{"uri":"The_Hunt_for_Red_October","surface_form":"novel of the same name","offset":267},{"uri":"Jack_Ryan_(film_series)","surface_form":"movie series","offset":319},{"uri":"Jack_Ryan_(character)","surface_form":"Jack Ryan","offset":353}]}